Package com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.api Description

The API of this framework. Every class inside this package provides necessary functionality for the framework, e.g. how arguments are parsed.

All classes inside this package can be extended to modify their behaviour. An instance of the extended class can then be passed to the JDACommandsBuilder to override the default behaviour.
